title: LOOK: Maxine Medina's Miss Universe national costume
text:
LOOK: Maxine Medina's Miss Universe national costume The headdress and earrings of Maxine Medina's costume cost more than P1M, according to designer Rhett Eala Published 11:41  41   MISS PHILIPPINES. Maxine Medina shows off her shining national costume at the Miss Universe pageant.   Miss Universe Philippines 2016 Maxine Medina shone at the pageant's preliminary rounds   26, and impressed fans with her glimmering national costume after. 
Maxine's costume was by Rhett Eala, who told ABS-CBN that its headdress and earrings cost more than P1 million, because of its South Sea pearls from Jewelmer. A video posted by Rhett Eala (@rhetteala) on Jan 26, 2017 at 6:01am PST 
Rhett also designed Maxine's evening gown for the pageant . 
The Miss Universe National Costume Presentation, which is filmed after the swimsuit and evening gown competitions,   candidates' scores in the pageant.
